---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Vera Makeup Artistry">
    <Header />
    <main class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-alabaster min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="text-neutral-900 border border-neutral-200 px-6 py-3 tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] uppercase font-bold mb-12 hover:bg-neutral-50 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-sm cursor-pointer">
                <i class="bi bi-x-lg"></i> Close & Return
            </a>
            <span class="text-taupe tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] uppercase font-bold mb-4 block">Legal</span>
            <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-neutral-900 mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>
            
            <div class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-loose max-w-none">
                <p class="mb-6">Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using our website.</p>
                
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mt-10 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">We collect information that you manually provide when filling out our booking inquiry forms, including your name, contact information, and event details. We also use third-party tools such as a chat plugin which may collect your IP address and chat interaction history.</p>
                
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mt-10 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">Your data is strictly used for the purpose of communicating with you about your event, providing makeup services, and improving our website experience. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
                
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mt-10 mb-4">3. Third-Party Tools</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">We may employ third-party companies and individuals to facilitate our website service (such as chat bots or hosting analytics) who have access to your personal data only to perform these tasks on our behalf.</p>

                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mt-10 mb-4">4. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:veramakeupvan@gmail.com" class="text-taupe hover:text-rosegold transition-colors underline underline-offset-4">veramakeupvan@gmail.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
</Layout>